\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw倉字係點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff3b09499f89ecb212245ca607eec729938a33d","tid":390152,"uid":18685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主要靠背. 要諗會好慢</blockquote><br />\n靠背代表你道行未夠<br />\n望到隻字 隻手放係keyboard 已經自動識打</blockquote><br />\n其實係<br />\n自然反應黎, 你諗到個字就知點樣拆, 隻手指就自然去左果個位度打落去<br />\n以前我都係用速成, 之後成功學到倉頡"},{"pid":"92c9ee7bf57c29ad3dac84eb59833baffc5e8a35","tid":390152,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主要靠背. 要諗會好慢</blockquote><br />\n靠背代表你道行未夠<br />\n望到隻字 隻手放係keyboard 已經自動識打</blockquote><br />\n我都係速成轉倉頡<br />\n喺公司練番嚟<br />\n打到咁上下其實已經唔洗諗點拆字<br />\n同事問起個字點打 我反而要望番keyboard答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa40c98c8251b62ecfcae2d4c6c327139f0481ba","tid":390152,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"做咩要轉"},{"pid":"f6034a73081e37f479472ed88d8eb601748141e2","tid":390152,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>主要靠背. 要諗會好慢</blockquote><br />\n靠背代表你道行未夠<br />\n望到隻字 隻手放係keyboard 已經自動識打</blockquote><br />\n我都係速成轉倉頡<br />\n喺公司練番嚟<br />\n打到咁上下其實已經唔洗諗點拆字<br />\n同事問起個字點打 我反而要望番keyboard答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你道行都未夠, <br />\n道行高係可以隨口up 英文碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 我唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0019ac6f35834e7d66442f27bb63b80e49de10fb","tid":390152,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"一年前我都轉咗, 用咗一個星期習慣晒<br />\n依家叫我打返速成都唔掂 <img src=\"/assets/fac