,"msg":"如果唔係智能電話嘅普及<br />\n我諗我有排都未學識倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8940fc8696b054fc01451b7545147b9735926e2","tid":390152,"uid":7121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"初初都係 五色學倉頡個app慢慢練<br />\n而加都叫做純熟<br />\n但係用慣電話打 用電腦都係慢少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae6a7452b89e730d2644a1fe0bebf3e315e53ca","tid":390152,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>主要靠背. 要諗會好慢</blockquote><br />\n靠背代表你道行未夠<br />\n望到隻字 隻手放係keyboard 已經自動識打</blockquote><br />\n我都係速成轉倉頡<br />\n喺公司練番嚟<br />\n打到咁上下其實已經唔洗諗點拆字<br />\n同事問起個字點打 我反而要望番keyboard答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你道行都未夠, <br />\n道行高係可以隨口up 英文碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 我唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n調轉晒，人地果種係唔駛經大腦已經打得出，要經一經英文字碼已經係隔左一重"},{"pid":"62cc0b9287170042b8001c4358cb62ec9b4e6323","tid":390152,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>主要靠背. 要諗會好慢</blockquote><br />\n靠背代表你道行未夠<br />\n望到隻字 隻手放係keyboard 已經自動識打</blockquote><br />\n我都係速成轉倉頡<br />\n喺公司練番嚟<br />\n打到咁上下其實已經唔洗諗點拆字<br />\n同事問起個字點打 我反而要望番keyboard答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你道行都未夠, <br />\n道行高係可以隨口up 英文碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 我唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n調轉晒，人地果種係唔駛經大腦已經打得出，要經一經英文字碼已經係隔左一重</blockquote><br />\n有啲似神經反射咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之呢個碼就係嗰隻字其中一part <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3638d332732996a25a19e6486a1d3d7800c5de63","tid":390152,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:10:32.000Z","msg":"第一步<br />\n移除速成輸入法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無決心嘅人係無辦法成功轉倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d5619472f29f621a1771f519e72b46a10ca0c2","tid":390152,"uid":74528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"小學用倉頡到而家22歲，轉翻速成反而要諗，慢慢啦，倉頡唔係一朝一夕可以學識，我而家都未係所有字識打哂"},{"pid":"00fcdcb96fd054aabb1462f98f675918f3964999","tid":390152,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://1drv.ms/t/s!AlILRscrYV3RsR5iOy31runrokgO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F1drv.ms%2Ft%2Fs%21AlILRscrYV3RsR5iOy31runrokgO&d=%2BnNreoHSAT5xh0CxqRKFYzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6e7f7a04\" target=\"_blank\">https://1drv.ms/t/s!AlILRscrYV3RsR5iOy31runrokgO</a><br />\n倉頡碼表，修改自~<br />\nname=泰瑞倉頡<br />\n，用~<br />\nkey=abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxy<br />\nwildcard=z<br />\n，可用xxzz打符號、用xzzzz打日文"},{"pid":"eeb55d523eb690cefa1e0971b570ee9001068a23","tid":390152,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一步<br />\n移除速成輸入法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無決心嘅人係無辦法成功轉倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n刪撚咗<br />\n用速成個陣打個「咗」都搵半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db494c9cdc5e3210d832ed30613ab7609408c4fe","tid":390152,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7c63e3b92c5148b19d771f729baca550d99e365","tid":390152,"uid":38968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年前我都轉咗, 用咗一個星期習慣晒<br />\n依家叫我打返速成都唔掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打速成比以前慢咗好多<br />\n如果打緊速成會唔覺意打咗倉頡"},{"pid":"f4079f623ba1ffb2592a7c19b662fc9916dd8c6c","tid":390152,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"其實電話打速成快好撚多, <br />\n打倉頡好撚慢"},{"pid":"d3edff952aed3eed219195f91bb34f16748b3b0c","tid":390152,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一步<br />\n移除速成輸入法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無決心嘅人係無辦法成功轉倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n刪撚咗<br />\n用速成個陣打個「咗」都搵半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n將手機中文輸入法default做倉頡<br />\n日日上連登逼自己打好快識</blockquote><br />\n只可以用空白格揀字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔可以喺字表揀，某啲字有同碼例外：「知」之類"},{"pid":"c74d2b02bdaff5b7aa730743a81712fe96a21e8b","tid":390152,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"我由第一日學就學倉頡， 真係好難回想當初打幾隻字都要半個鐘既慘況"},{"pid":"db949b5d981f3d4bf1658617a5882b4e82fee85f","tid":390152,"uid":50642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"轉咗打倉頡好耐<br />\n依家要我打返速成會唔識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ada4fd6495dd063c49613475ab810b06641dfa","tid":390152,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f4a1c58de2d5e44f49bff033bf7cbd9909d8661","tid":390152,"uid":60131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:06:22.000Z","msg":"之前打速成10年，轉打倉頡都有10年，而家打速成會變烏龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由速成轉倉頡比較簡單，只要熟習返拆碼方法就得，仲少咗揀字嘅煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5c0984f0affbf4efd79e34075e551e45a88b22","tid":390152,"uid":3216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"以前部notebook keyboard 無中文標示<br />\n打速成搵唔到邊粒掣<br />\n後來焗轉倉頡<br />\n而家好爽"},{"pid":"6e48858b9939177525ea3ed53c7451f0d442b94b","tid":390152,"uid":18685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實電話打速成快好撚多, <br />\n打倉頡好撚慢</blockquote><br />\n唔係啦<br />\n你打完速成要搵字<br />\n打倉頡就直接打左果個字出黎"},{"pid":"fb2e4842c4e4a8cbedf7a38cde26419762f344f6","tid":390152,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實電話打速成快好撚多, <br />\n打倉頡好撚慢</blockquote><br />\n唔係啦<br />\n你打完速成要搵字<br />\n打倉頡就直接打左果個字出黎</blockquote><br />\n有常用字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  第一個就係"},{"pid":"81946558e7f4e8d30533433ac6e3377747accf38","tid":390152,"uid":18685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實電話打速成快好撚多, <br />\n打倉頡好撚慢</blockquote><br />\n唔係啦<br />\n你打完速成要搵字<br />\n打倉頡就直接打左果個字出黎</blockquote><br />\n有常用字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  第一個就係</blockquote><br />\n非常用字咪要慢慢搵囉<br />\n你打D MSG唔會全部都係一式一樣呱"},{"pid":"8edfed9c8a551a4b8c3d07a60412bc39ebc71d15","tid":390152,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實電話打速成快好撚多, <br />\n打倉頡好撚慢</blockquote><br />\n唔係啦<br />\n你打完速成要搵字<br />\n打倉頡就直接打左果個字出黎</blockquote><br />\n有常用字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  第一個就係</blockquote><br />\n佢嘅世界，打字嘅用途就係攞嚟send message<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}